<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>RedRunner</title>
  <!-- Leaflet -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://cdn.leafletjs.com/leaflet-0.7.5/leaflet.css" />
  <script src="http://cdn.leafletjs.com/leaflet-0.7.5/leaflet.js"></script>


  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
  <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="http://cartodb.com/assets/favicon.ico" />
  <style>
      html, body, #map {
          height: 100%;
          padding: 0;
          margin: 0;
      }
  </style>

  <%= favicon_link_tag 'logo.png' %>
</head>
<body>

<%= render 'layouts/header' %>
<%= yield %>
<%= render 'layouts/footer' %>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <h2 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <h4>Is there a fee for using RedRunner?</h4>
        <p>No. RedRunner is freely available for use by everyone.</p><br>

        <h4>Do I need to register in order to spectate?</h4>
        <p>No. Racers are the only ones required to register for tracking purposes.</p><br>

        <h4>Is the mobile app safe to use?</h4>
        <p>It's safe. We promise.</p><br>

        <h4>Help! I can't install the app on my phone!</h4>
        <p>The RedRunner APK is a non-market application, so you may have to change your security
        settings to allow the installation of non-market apps. You can do this by navigating to
        <i>settings > security > allow installation of non-market apps</i>. You must do this BEFORE you download the APK
        from the RedRunner website.</p><br>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
